                <h2>My Hobbies and Interests</h2>
                <p>Aside from my piano, I enjoy a doing a variety of things in my life. Throughout school, I used to play basketball all the time for fun. 
                    I would play the sport with my friends and better my skills through casual play. Since coming to university, I havent been 
                    able to play the game anymore which I am sad about.

                    One interest of mine that I've picked up since coming to university would be singing in acapellla. I intially joined this 
                    society to fill out the requirements in my performance course, but I gradually came to love singing with them and I always look forawrd 
                    to our rehearsals.
